Plan.Description: The Golden Model is another one our of newest models, a multi generational home. The home includes an additional suite, complete with a mini kitchenette, a full bath with a curb less shower, a living/bedroom space and private entrance, perfect for housing a caregiver, visiting family, and the occasional mother-in-law. In addition to being a man cave or office space due to the privacy that is offered. The home is defined by the open floor plan, complimented by the custom tile work and plant shelving throughout the home.

The Vail Model is an exciting new model that we have added to our floor plans that features a grand open feel with tray ceilings, incorporating the dining area and kitchen with a huge island and living room as an all-in-one room, perfect for the couple that loves to entertain. Custom tile work throughout complete this home.

The Montrose Model, with an open floor plan with its large windows and vaulted ceilings give this home a warm and comfortable feeling. With the family area, dining and kitchen all open and connected, it is a true "great room". A showcase of elegance and design for the home owner that wants to enjoy all the comforts of a home that exceeds their expectations.

The Durango Model is one of our most popular floor plan that encompasses a very comfortable and inviting floor design that enhances natural light and a simple quality. From the spacious inviting living room with vaulted ceilings that carry into the open concept kitchen and dining room combination. The Durango boasts a large master bedroom suite with a master bath featuring dual vanity sinks , a walk-in shower and a walk-in closet. Custom tile work throughout complete this home.

The Sheridan Model is an exciting new model that we have added to our floor plans that features a grand open feel with tray ceilings, incorporating the dining area and kitchen with a huge island and living room as an all-in-one room, perfect for the couple that loves to entertain. Complete with custom tile work throughout.

The Monarch Model is our showcase of quality and design. A very versatile floor plan that can be customized to fit your needs. The large open kitchen is a gathering place for family and friends with its vast windows and sliding glass doors that open up to the large covered patio, perfect for entertaining guests. The Monarch is completed with custom tile work and vaulted ceilings.
